              <div class="photo-spot__info">
                <div class="photo-spot__name">浅草寺·雷门</div>
                <div class="photo-spot__type">标志性大灯笼</div>
              </div>
              <div class="photo-spot__best-time">⏰ 清晨 6-7 点</div>
            </div>
            <div class="photo-spot__details">
              <div class="photo-spot__position">
                <span class="photo-spot__position-label">📍 最佳站位</span>
                <span>正面中轴线，退到仲見世通入口处，纳入雷门全景 + 远处仁王门</span>
              </div>
              <div class="photo-spot__tips">
                <span class="photo-spot__tips-label">✨ 技巧</span>
                <span>清晨无人，利用晨光从东方打来的侧光，灯笼颜色更鲜艳。雨天拍地面倒影效果绝佳。节日会挂特别灯笼，可提前查询日历。</span>
              </div>
              <div class="photo-spot__composition">
                <span class="photo-spot__composition-label">🖼️ 构图</span>
                <span>三分法纵置：灯笼占左三分之一，天空背景留三分之二；低角度仰拍可强调灯笼气势</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="photo-spot">
            <div class="photo-spot__header">
              <span class="photo-spot__number">02</span>
              <div class="photo-spot__info">
                <div class="photo-spot__name">新宿御苑·樱花草坪</div>
                <div class="photo-spot__type">樱花季专属</div>
              </div>
              <div class="photo-spot__best-time">⏰ 9-11 点（樱花季3-4月）</div>
            </div>
            <div class="photo-spot__details">
              <div class="photo-spot__position">
                <span class="photo-spot__position-label">📍 最佳站位</span>
                <span>新宿门入场后左转，大草坪北侧边缘，以蓝天或远处树林为背景拍樱花树冠</span>
              </div>
              <div class="photo-spot__tips">
                <span class="photo-spot__tips-label">✨ 技巧</span>
                <span>工作日人少，樱花盛开高峰期避开周末。顺光拍（背对太阳）花色粉嫩；逆光拍（面对太阳）花瓣透光梦幻。带毛毯坐在草坪仰拍花瓣，极具代入感。</span>
              </div>
              <div class="photo-spot__composition">
                <span class="photo-spot__composition-label">🖼️ 构图</span>
                <span>从草坪低角度仰拍，人物坐在花下，樱花枝条自然延伸作为框架；或远景全树+人物1/3处的人景关系构图</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="photo-spot">
            <div class="photo-spot__header">
              <span class="photo-spot__number">03</span>
              <div class="photo-spot__info">
                <div class="photo-spot__name">涩谷十字路口</div>
                <div class="photo-spot__type">城市街拍</div>
              </div>
              <div class="photo-spot__best-time">⏰ 夜间 19-21 点</div>
            </div>
            <div class="photo-spot__details">
              <div class="photo-spot__position">
                <span class="photo-spot__position-label">📍 最佳站位</span>
                <span>①路口中央斑马线上（绿灯时随人流进入）②Scramble Square 二楼观景台（免费，需消费）③星巴克旁的二楼窗口</span>
              </div>
              <div class="photo-spot__tips">
                <span class="photo-spot__tips-label">✨ 技巧</span>
                <span>夜晚霓虹灯配合行人流量最壮观；雨天地面倒影是加分项。用手机的连拍模式抓人流光轨；三脚架+长曝光（1/15s）可拍出模糊行人的流动感。</span>
              </div>
              <div class="photo-spot__composition">
                <span class="photo-spot__composition-label">🖼️ 构图</span>
                <span>俯拍全景展现十字路口规模；平拍强调人流与霓虹；广角镜头涵盖四周广告牌形成包围感</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="photo-spot">
            <div class="photo-spot__header">
